Continue understanding the details of the outstanding regulatory tasks for the coming 3 to 4 days.  If the above opinion is still the same, then the suggested communication to Wade (preferably from you) is "if there is renegotiation, then GA shall send the required person/persons on a semi-full time basis, if arbitration, then GA shall be available on as needed basis".  

Caveat:
